SELECT "product_category"."id", "product_category"."name", "product_category"."parent_id", "product_category"."lft", "product_category"."rght", "product_category"."tree_id", "product_category"."level", T2."id", T2."name", T2."parent_id", T2."lft", T2."rght", T2."tree_id", T2."level" FROM "product_category" INNER JOIN "product_category" T2 ON ("product_category"."parent_id" = T2."id") WHERE "product_category"."parent_id" IN (?)

UPDATE "product_category"
            SET "lft" = CASE
                    WHEN "lft" > ?
                        THEN "lft" + ?
                    ELSE "lft" END,
                "rght" = CASE
                    WHEN "rght" > ?
                        THEN "rght" + ?
                    ELSE "rght" END
            WHERE "tree_id" = ?
              AND ("lft" > ? OR "rght" > ?)
